172 A.3d 1087 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. KYREE T. JOHNSON, A/K/A KYRE JOHNSON, KYREE JAQUAN JOHNSON, TYREE JOHNSON, AND JOHNSON TYREE, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-316 September Term 2017

079655 November 14, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003796-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
